  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Primary objective:

      To compare the effects of short term therapy post total knee replacement (TKR) between a
      hydrotherapy treatment group and a physiotherapy treatment group.

      Secondary objectives:

      To compare the effects of short term therapy post total knee replacement (TKR) between a
      hydrotherapy treatment group and a physiotherapy treatment group based on measurements of
      timed up and go (TUG, as primary outcome), range of motion, pain and quality of life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
